    "description": "The KoolSpan Lock is a VHS-Cassette sized device that authenticates users and bridges their Ethernet traffic onto the network. It contains an embedded Smart Card and cryptographic processor. The case is tamper-resistant. Each Lock can support up to 512 simultaneous users each with 256-bit AES encryption. The Lock supports a \"Keyless Exchange\" and provides both Wi-Fi security and Remote Access (VPN) connections.",
